### Hello!
My name is Andreas Georgiou. I am currently a third year computer science student at University of Bristol. I love technology, computers and maths. I am particularly interested in cryptography, computational neuroscience and artificial intelligence. Up for a chat? Contact me via any of the means below. (This page is still under construction)
